## 4. Key Summary Table

| Feature | ARP | Telnet | SSH |
|---|---|---|---|
| Goal | Find MAC address | Remote Access | Secure Remote Access |
| Port | N/A | 23 | 22 |
| OSI Layer | Layer 2 | Layer 7 | Layer 7 |
| Security | None (Trusting) | None (Plain Text) | High (Encrypted) |

